      <url>/2022/11/23/%E9%9F%A6%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%BF/Unit1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Unit1"><a href="#Unit1" class="headerlink" title="Unit1"></a>Unit1</h3><h4 id="BENE"><a href="#BENE" class="headerlink" title="BENE"></a>BENE</h4><p>​    Latin for “well”</p><ul><li><strong>benefit</strong>    n：益处    v：受益    </li></ul><p>​        动词：<strong>benefit from</strong>    从……中受益</p><p>​        benefit of true love，or friends with benefits（sex） ？</p><p>​        the benefit of a formal college education 上正式大学的好处</p><p>​        a benefit concert    慈善演唱会</p><p>​                                                                <img src="https://picgo-1314705274.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/picgo/%E9%9F%A6%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%BF1.1-1.png" alt="im        age-20221122235507620" style="zoom: 67%;"></p><ul><li><strong>beneficial</strong>    adj.</li></ul><p>​        A good diet is beneficial to health</p><ul><li><strong>benefactor</strong>    /ˈbenɪfæktə(r)/    捐助人</li></ul><p>​        bene——好，factor——要素，benefactor——提供好的要素者。</p><p>​        A benefactor of the arts    艺术家的赞助者。（在未成名之前往往需要人赞助才能维持生活）</p><ul><li><strong>beneficiary</strong>    /ˌbenɪˈfɪʃəri/    受益人</li></ul><p>​        the beneficiary of will    遗嘱的受益人</p><p>​        the beneficiary of early election    早期选举的受益人</p><p>​        the beneficiary of new era    新时代的受益人</p><ul><li><strong>benign</strong>    /bɪˈnaɪn/    和善的；良性的</li></ul><p>​        a more benign audience    一位更和善的观众</p><p>​        an especially benign climate 一种特别怡人的气候</p><p>​        a benign tumour 一个良性肿瘤</p><ul><li><strong>benevolent</strong>    /bəˈnevələnt/    仁慈的；和蔼的</li></ul><p>​        a very benevolent employer    一个非常仁慈的老板（不会让你天天加班996）</p><ul><li><strong>benevolence</strong>    noun form</li></ul><p>​        the benevolence of the employer moved every one    老板的仁慈打动了每一个人</p><ul><li><strong>bonus</strong>    奖金；<em>额外收获</em>（没有这个收获也照样能活，额外收获的bonus是一个附加奖励，不是核心）</li></ul><p>​        North sea oil has proved a bonus for British technology    </p><ul><li><strong>bonanza</strong>    /bəˈnænzə/    富含矿藏的地带；财运亨通</li></ul><p>​        a benanza year    财运亨通、赚大钱的年（风口来了，猪都能飞的那种）</p><p>​        a benanza year for the oil industry</p><ul><li><strong>bounty</strong>    /ˈbaʊnti/     赏金；丰富之物</li></ul><p>​        bounty hunter 赏金猎人</p><p>​        autumn’s bounty of fruits    秋天丰盛的水果</p><ul><li><strong>benediction</strong>    祷告；祝福（一般用于宗教场合）</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
